    "Almost all of Mira works without our servers: writing, mood, photos, search, iCloud sync, themes, the on-device AI. The cloud features (Ask Mira and weekly reflections through the Cloud option) talk to external servers and may be intermittently slow or blocked on Russian networks due to regulatory restrictions on outbound services. If you run into that, switch to the on-device AI in Settings → Intelligence — it runs entirely on your iPhone and doesn't depend on any external service.": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Almost all of Mira works without our servers: writing, mood, photos, search, iCloud sync, themes, the on-device AI. The cloud features (Ask Mira and weekly reflections through the Cloud option) talk to external servers and may be intermittently slow or blocked on Russian networks due to regulatory restrictions on outbound services. If you run into that, switch to the on-device AI in Settings → Intelligence — it runs entirely on your iPhone and doesn't depend on any external service."
          }
        },
        "ru": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Почти всё в Mira работает без наших серверов: записи, настроение, фото, поиск, iCloud-синк, темы, локальный AI. Облачные функции (Ask Mira и еженедельные рефлексии в режиме Cloud) обращаются к внешним серверам и на российских сетях из-за ограничений на работу зарубежных сервисов могут работать с перебоями или быть недоступны. Если столкнулись с этим — переключитесь на локальный AI в Настройки → Интеллект: он работает прямо на iPhone и не зависит от внешних сервисов."
          }
        }
      }
    },
